      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 111,
      "message": "NB: This part of the code has been repeated 3 times. Thus, you can extract it into a private method like this:\n\nprivate ResponseEntity<String> validateAndReturnSuccess(String dataspaceName, String anchorName, String parentNodeXpath, String nodeData, String contentTypeInHeader) {\n    final ContentType contentType = ContentType.fromString(contentTypeInHeader);\n    cpsDataService.validateData(dataspaceName, anchorName, parentNodeXpath, nodeData, contentType);\n    return ResponseEntity.ok().build();\n}\n\nThen, can make a call to it;\n    if (Boolean.TRUE.equals(dryRunEnabled)) {\n        return validateAndReturnSuccess(dataspaceName, anchorName, parentNodeXpath, nodeData, contentTypeInHeader);\n    } else { ...\n    \n    }",
